  "authorEmail": "simon@simondorfman.com",
  "notes": "Philosophy:\nKill champions, attack & raze realms.\n\nRealms:\nBirthright for Taxation rule. Last digit of 9 for Lady Luck combo.\nChamps:\nCleric casters/dragons/AD&D. Flyer/earthwalk. Abyss powers for recycling.\nCombos:\n-A Good Defense + Jerome = retrieve offensive spells.\n-Avanil + Atonement = draw 5 more cards or keep realm in play for win\n-Rengarth Oracle + Lady Luck = put a realm at the top with a high last digit with Rengarth so that Lady Luck gives allows an extra realm can be played into the formation\n-Espionage! + Lady Luck = put a level zero card at the top of opponent's deck so I get to play or at least draw my top card.\n-Marco Volo + Lady Luck/The Fates = either look at my own top card or theirs depending on if i want to draw cards or force them to discard.\n-Ethereal Champion + cast Earthquake in battle = win battle and raze opponents realm",
